<span id="freeTextContainer948927375534422844">Funny, I know that. I just can&apos;t remember if he&apos;s the one who wrote the story about the man who fell in love with a gorilla. Also, I can&apos;t remember who wrote All my friends are up and dressed and dying. It has bothered me for some time. I believe I shall cease this palaver and go to yahoo and investigate.<br/>Cheery-bye.<br/></span>
  <span id="freeText948927375534422844" style="display:none">Funny, I know that. I just can't remember if he's the one who wrote the story about the man who fell in love with a gorilla. Also, I can't remember who wrote All my friends are up and dressed and dying. It has bothered me for some time. I believe I shall cease this palaver and go to yahoo and investigate.<br />Cheery-bye.<br /></span>
