<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer11860594776083490812">Sidney Joseph Perelman, almost always known as S. J. Perelman, was a Jewish-American humorist, author, and screenwriter. He is best known for his humorous short pieces written over many years for <i>The New Yorker</i>. He also wrote for several other magazines, as well as books, scripts, and screenplays.</span>

</div>
